<body>
   <p> The width (and height) of the element below is <b>260px</b>. </p>
   <p> Calculation: <b>200px</b> (width) + <b>20px</b> (padding left) + <b>20px</b> (padding right) + <b>10px</b> (border left) + <b>10px</b> (border right) = <b>260px</b> </p>
